	{ title: 'Chinese Green Bean Stir-Fry', difficulty: 2, time: 35, servings: 40, description: 'Asian-style green beans with lots of flavor! This recipe is made for a large party; but can be scaled down for a family dinner. Serve cold or warm.', 
