	{ title: 'Cantonese Style Pork and Shrimp Dumplings', difficulty: 3, time: 50, servings: 10, description: 'I love dumplings and have come up with this recipe using all ingredients that I like. The dumplings consist of pork, shrimp, watercress, water chestnuts, and assorted seasonings, and they are absolutely delicious!', 
